folder: Fresh Pond Road & Gates Avenue, Queens, NY
original_title: Queens: Fresh Pond Road - Gates Avenue
text:
(old No.) 684 Fresh Pond Road (tracks thereon), at the S.W. corner of Gates Ave., showing the G. Hulst farmhouse in a set of four views.  The owners were G. Hulst 1852-1860, and E.T. Hulst 1873-1896. It was demolished in March 1925.

March 1923.
Views 1 & 3.
Views 2 & 4: 1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
